first:
please read the instructions on https://github.com/tzlr-de/LEPY

second:
- you should start your Anaconda environment with the installation of LEPY
- change the working directory to the main.py script in the LEPY folder
- execute LepyLoop's LLmain.py by executing "python3 /path/to/LLmain.py"

third:
- LepyLoop will ask you for an input directoy. Please state the directory that contains the images to be analysed.
- LepyLoop will ask for the number of individuals to be processed per run. We recommend 100. If you experience issues on your machine, try a low number
